instructions:
Pour anisette into chilled cocktail glass, swirl to coat inside;
discard remaining anisette. Shake remaining ingredients with ice
and strain into glass.

Pour creme de violette into chilled cocktail glass and swirl to coat;
discard excess liqueur. Shake remaining ingredients with ice and
strain into glass.

Fill hurricane or parfait glass with ice. Pour grenadine over ice;
add bourbon. Shake remaining ingredients with ice and pour slowly
into glass. Garnish with peach.
